Jeremiah Moss, who runs the blog called "Jeremiah's Disappearing New York" (subtitled "The Book of Complaints: A Bitter Nostalgic View of the Extinct City"), has published part of the city history talk about Extra Place, which was published in the journal "The New York in 1952.
